{"id":2556,"date":"2022-04-25T15:08:58","date_gmt":"2022-04-25T12:08:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.newsdgtl.com\/?p=2556"},"modified":"2022-04-25T15:08:58","modified_gmt":"2022-04-25T12:08:58","slug":"the-nft-platform-from-animoca-planet-hollywood","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.newsdgtl.com\/the-nft-platform-from-animoca-planet-hollywood\/","title":{"rendered":"The NFT Platform From Animoca &#038; Planet Hollywood"},"content":{"rendered":"<p> <br \/>\n<\/p>\n<div itemprop=\"mainEntityOfPage\">\n<p>Animoca Brands has teamed up with star-studded hospitality franchise Planet Hollywood to form \u2018<a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/meta_hollywood\">MetaHollywood<\/a>\u2019. Within the joint venture will be a mass collection of NFTs, as well as a wider community-driven metaverse platform.<\/p>\n<p>The MetaHollywood NFT collections will include 60,000 assets, with each depicting an iconic piece of memorabilia (whether that be a photograph, movie poster, or iconic fashion item) from a <strong>Hollywood-produced blockbuster<\/strong>. Films from all eras will feature in the collection, with NFTs based on characters played by the likes of Arnold Schwarznegger, Michael J. Fox, Jim Carrey, Scarlett Johansson, and many more, to be expected.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>In addition to its NFT endeavour, MetaHollywood will also create a movie-centric NFT marketplace, where studios and creators can sell NFTs such as behind-the-scenes clips to fans. It will also launch \u2018HWOOD,\u2019 a native utility and governance token which will allow holders to influence decisions over community development. That being said, only 0.5% of the token\u2019s supply will go up for <strong>public sale<\/strong>, as 12% will be allocated to the project\u2019s marketing fund, and 10% will go to the fashion and content development fund for purchasing licensing rights.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>In commenting on the company\u2019s monumental (and first) plunge into Web3, Robert Earl, founder of\u00a0Planet Hollywood, had this to say:<i> \u201cI am thrilled to partner with Animoca Brands as we launch Planet Hollywood into the metaverse. The universal appeal of film, along with our unprecedented collection of iconic memorabilia, make the possibilities limitless. Through MetaHollywood, we will offer utility and functionality that is unrivaled in this burgeoning sector, and I cannot wait to see what our users create using the power of their imagination\u201d.\u00a0<\/i><\/p>\n<p><b>Sign up to the project\u2019s whitelist &gt;&gt; <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/metahollywood.io\/\">Here<\/a><\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>Want more? Connect with NFT Plazas<\/b><\/p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/mailchi.mp\/ecadf05eb1bf\/1\">Join the Weekly Newsletter<br \/><\/a><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/discord.gg\/qSQwMaM\">Join our Discord<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/nftplazas\">Follow us on Twitter<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/nftplazas\">Like us on Facebook<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/nftplazas\/\">Follow us on Instagram<\/a><\/p>\n<p><small><em>*All investment\/financial opinions expressed by NFT Plazas are from the personal research and experience of our site moderators and are intended as educational material only. Individuals are required to fully research any product prior to making any kind of investment.<\/em><\/small><\/p>\n<div class=\"saboxplugin-wrap\" itemtype=\"http:\/\/schema.org\/Person\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"author\">\n<div class=\"saboxplugin-tab\">\n<div class=\"saboxplugin-gravatar\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"saboxplugin-desc\">\n<div ite